; font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;如图所示轻质光滑定滑轮，&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;M1=2kg&lt;/span&gt;，&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;M2=1kg&lt;/span&gt;，离地高度为&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;H=O.5m&lt;/span&gt;．&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;M1&lt;/span&gt;与&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;M2&lt;/span&gt;从静止开始释放，不计一切阻力&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;g=10m/s2&lt;/span&gt;，由静止下落了&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;0.3n&lt;/span&gt;时的速度大小为（　　）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体;color:black'&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;p class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;&lt;img width=78 height=105 src=&quot;/Public/tikupics/20151204/20/28/566186f885ab41449232120.gif&quot; v:shapes=&quot;_x0000_i1025&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; ";s:6:"clicks";N;s:11:"source_name";s:87:"2014-2015学年河南省信阳市淮滨二高高三（上）第三次月考物理试卷";s:13:"difficulty_id";s:1:"3";}i:3;a:6:{s:2:"id";s:6:"236318";s:7:"options";s:481:"["\u5c0f\u7403\u81ea\u7531\u4e0b\u843d\uff0c\u843d\u5728\u7ad6\u76f4\u5f39\u7c27\u4e0a\uff0c\u5c06\u5f39\u7c27\u538b\u7f29\u540e\u53c8\u88ab\u5f39\u7c27\u5f39\u8d77\u6765","\u62c9\u7740\u7269\u4f53\u6cbf\u5149\u6ed1\u7684\u659c\u9762\u5300\u901f\u4e0a\u5347","\u8df3\u4f1e\u8fd0\u52a8\u5458\u5f20\u5f00\u4f1e\u540e\uff0c\u5728\u7a7a\u4e2d\u5300\u901f\u4e0b\u964d","\u98de\u884c\u7684\u5b50\u5f39\u51fb\u4e2d\u653e\u5728\u5149\u6ed1\u6c34\u5e73\u684c\u9762\u4e0a\u7684\u6728\u5757"]";s:7:"content";s:601:" &lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt; font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;下面的实例中，系统机械能守恒的是（　　）&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;     &lt;p class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;; color:black'&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; ";s:6:"clicks";N;s:11:"source_name";s:108:"2014-2015学年江苏省盐城市东台市创新学校高二（上）第二次月考物理试卷（必修）";s:13:"difficulty_id";s:1:"2";}i:4;a:6:{s:2:"id";s:6:"236319";s:7:"options";s:64:"["\ufe63mgh","mg\uff08H\ufe63h\uff09","mg\uff08H+h\uff09","mgH"]";s:7:"content";s:1147:" &lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt; font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;桌面高为&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;h&lt;/span&gt;，质量为&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;m&lt;/span&gt;的小球从离桌面高&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;H&lt;/span&gt;处由静止自由落下，不计空气阻力，设桌面处的重力势能为零，则小球落地前瞬间的机械能为（　　）&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;p class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;&lt;img width=152 height=119 src=&quot;/Public/tikupics/20151204/20/28/566186f8ea8141449232120.gif&quot; alt=&quot; &quot; v:shapes=&quot;_x0000_i1025&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;; color:black'&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; ";s:6:"clicks";N;s:11:"source_name";s:108:"2014-2015学年江苏省盐城市东台市创新学校高二（上）第二次月考物理试卷（必修）";s:13:"difficulty_id";s:1:"2";}i:5;a:6:{s:2:"id";s:6:"236320";s:7:"options";s:301:"["\u5f39\u7c27\u7684\u5f39\u6027\u52bf\u80fd\u5148\u589e\u5927\u540e\u51cf\u5c0f","\u5c0f\u7403\u7684\u52a8\u80fd\u5148\u589e\u5927\u540e\u51cf\u5c0f","\u5c0f\u7403\u7684\u91cd\u529b\u52bf\u80fd\u5148\u589e\u5927\u540e\u51cf\u5c0f","\u673a\u68b0\u80fd\u603b\u548c\u5148\u589e\u5927\u540e\u51cf\u5c0f"]";s:7:"content";s:1074:" &lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt; font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;如图所示，小球从高处下落到竖直放置的轻弹簧上，那么小球从接触弹簧开始到将弹簧压缩到最短的过程中（弹簧一直保持竖直），下列关于能的叙述正确的是（　　）&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;p class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;&lt;img width=62 height=88 src=&quot;/Public/tikupics/20151204/20/28/566186f9146531449232121.gif&quot; alt=&quot; &quot; v:shapes=&quot;_x0000_i1025&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;p class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;; color:black'&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; ";s:6:"clicks";N;s:11:"source_name";s:108:"2014-2015学年江苏省盐城市东台市创新学校高二（上）第二次月考物理试卷（必修）";s:13:"difficulty_id";s:1:"2";}i:6;a:6:{s:2:"id";s:6:"236321";s:7:"options";s:265:"["\u5c0f\u7403\u52a8\u80fd\u5148\u51cf\u5c0f\u540e\u589e\u5927","\u5c0f\u7403\u52a8\u80fd\u4e00\u76f4\u51cf\u5c0f","\u5c0f\u7403\u91cd\u529b\u52bf\u80fd\u5148\u589e\u5927\u540e\u51cf\u5c0f","\u5c0f\u7403\u91cd\u529b\u52bf\u80fd\u5148\u51cf\u5c0f\u540e\u589e\u5927"]";s:7:"content";s:1050:" &lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt; font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;如图所示，细绳悬挂一个小球在竖直平面内来回摆动，在小球从&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;P&lt;/span&gt;点向&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;Q&lt;/span&gt;点运动的过程中（　　）&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;p class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;&lt;img width=129 height=98 src=&quot;/Public/tikupics/20151204/20/28/566186f933a5a1449232121.gif&quot; alt=&quot; &quot; v:shapes=&quot;_x0000_i1025&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;p class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;; color:black'&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; ";s:6:"clicks";N;s:11:"source_name";s:108:"2014-2015学年江苏省盐城市东台市创新学校高二（上）第二次月考物理试卷（必修）";s:13:"difficulty_id";s:1:"2";}i:7;a:6:{s:2:"id";s:6:"236322";s:7:"options";s:33:"["5.0 m","1.8 m","3.6 m","7.2 m"]";s:7:"content";s:1426:" &lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt; font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;蹦床运动要求运动员在一张绷紧的弹性网上蹦起、腾空并做空中动作．为了测量运动员跃起的高度，训练时如图&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;可在弹性网上安装压力传感器，利用传感器记录弹性网的压力，并在计算机上做出压力﹣时间如图&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;，假设做出的图象如图所示．设运动员在空中运动时可视为质点，则运动员跃起的最大高度为（&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;g&lt;/span&gt;取&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;10m/s2&lt;/span&gt;）（　　）&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;p class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;&lt;img width=243 height=116 src=&quot;/Public/tikupics/20151204/20/28/566186f9507511449232121.gif&quot; alt=&quot; &quot; v:shapes=&quot;_x0000_i1025&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;; color:black'&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; ";s:6:"clicks";N;s:11:"source_name";s:87:"2014-2015学年江苏省南通市启东中学高二（上）第二次月考物理试卷";s:13:"difficulty_id";s:1:"3";}i:8;a:6:{s:2:"id";s:6:"236323";s:7:"options";s:217:"["\u5300\u901f\u5de1\u822a\u7684\u65e0\u4eba\u673a","\u7f13\u6162\u4e0b\u964d\u7684\u70ed\u6c14\u7403","\u6cbf\u5149\u6ed1\u66f2\u9762\u4e0b\u6ed1\u7684\u7269\u5757","\u52a0\u901f\u4e0b\u6f5c\u7684\u6838\u6f5c\u8247"]";s:7:"content";s:605:" &lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt; font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;下列运动过程中，物体的机械能守恒的是（　　）&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;p class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;; color:black'&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; ";s:6:"clicks";N;s:11:"source_name";s:87:"2014-2015学年江苏省南通市启东中学高二（上）第二次月考物理试卷";s:13:"difficulty_id";s:1:"1";}i:9;a:6:{s:2:"id";s:6:"236324";s:7:"options";s:253:"["\u91cd\u529b\u5bf9\u5c0f\u7403\u505a\u6b63\u529f","\u5f39\u7c27\u5bf9\u5c0f\u7403\u4e0d\u505a\u529f","\u5c0f\u7403\u7684\u673a\u68b0\u80fd\u5b88\u6052","\u5c0f\u7403\u51cf\u5c11\u7684\u91cd\u529b\u52bf\u80fd\u5168\u90e8\u8f6c\u5316\u4e3a\u52a8\u80fd"]";s:7:"content";s:1166:" &lt;span style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt; font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;轻质弹簧一端固定在&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;O&lt;/span&gt;点，另一端拴一个小球．现把小球拉到与&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;O&lt;/span&gt;点等高的位置（此时弹簧处于自然长度）静止释放，在小球摆到&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;O&lt;/span&gt;点正下方的过程中（　　）&lt;span lang=EN-US&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;p class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;&lt;img width=93 height=97 src=&quot;/Public/tikupics/20151204/20/28/566186fa077811449232122.gif&quot; alt=&quot; &quot; v:shapes=&quot;_x0000_i1025&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;     &lt;p class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt;font-family:宋体;color:black'&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p class=MsoNormal&gt;&lt;span lang=EN-US style='font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;; color:black'&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; ";s:6:"clicks";N;s:11:"source_name";s:87:"2014-2015学年江苏省南通市启东中学高二（上）第二次月考物理试卷";s:13:"difficulty_id";s:1:"3";}}
